Apollo Investment Corporation (AINV) and StoneCastle Financial Corp (BANX) Financial Review

					Posted by Tristan Rich on Jul 18th, 2017 // No Comments 




StoneCastle Financial Corp (NASDAQ: BANX) and Apollo Investment Corporation (NASDAQ:AINV) are both small-cap finance companies, but which is the superior stock? We will compare the two businesses based on the strength of their analyst recommendations, institutional ownership, risk, valuation, profitabiliy, dividends and earnings. 
Analyst Recommendations


 Get StoneCastle Financial Corp alerts:



